Botafogo        2-1  Ypiranga

[Jan 18]
Fluminense      4-2  AA Bahia

[Jan 25]
Fluminense     W0-0  Ypiranga

[Jan 27]
Internacional   1-1  Sul América


 1. Botafogo          10  8  1  1  24- 5  17   Finalists
 2. Fluminense        10  8  1  1  20- 6  17   Finalists
---------------------------------------------
 3. Ypiranga          10  5  1  4  17- 8  11
 4. AA Bahia          10  3  0  7  12-23   6
 5. Sul América       10  1  3  6   7-19   5
 6. Internacional     10  1  2  7   7-26   4

Note: At the time, there were no tie-breaking criteria; therefore, Botafogo and Fluminense
had to play a Final to vie for the 1919 title.


Final

[Feb 24, 1920]
Botafogo 1-1  Fluminense

[May 23]
Botafogo        1-0  Fluminense


Botafogo Sport Club (Salvador) are champions of Bahia 1919.



